
#@since 1.8.2

= class Rinda::SimpleRenewer < Object
include DRbUndumped

An SimpleRenewer allows a TupleSpace to check if a TupleEntry is
still alive.

== Class Methods

--- new(sec = 180)

Creates a new SimpleRenewer that keeps an object alive for another
+sec+ seconds.

== Instance Methods

--- renew

Called by the TupleSpace to check if the object is still alive.

#@end
